data.description: Welcome home to this custom 4 Br 4 1/2 Bth 2 story colonial style home w/master-on-main, finished terrace level w/3 car garage, & in-ground pool w/covered cabana on 2+ acres. Exterior offers dbl covered front porch, 2nd driveway, & manicured lawn. Main ~ Formal living-rm & dining-rm, open kitchen w/custom cabinetry, granite, SS, breakfast, and 2 story family room w/stone fireplace. Master offers sep shower, dbl sink, jetted jacuzzi tub & large closet. Generous size secondary bedrooms. Terrace ~ equipped w/kitchenette, living-rm, rec room, full bath, & bonus (5th BR)
